Paul Vaughn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Vaughn 0 Paul Vaughn is an American actor, most notable for his recurring role as "Paul" on ten episodes of the American situation comedy Cheers. He also made guest appearances on television series including Fantasy Island, Three's a Crowd and I Dream of Jeannie.
